Date: Mon, 18 Nov 2024 10:31:58 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Normalize geometry collection geo shapes provided as object
 literals

Transform geometry collection to MultiPoint or MultiPoligon if possible.
This alignes it with WKT string behavior
